title: Cloning - 1999 - Khun Copy Khun - Thai Movie

sources.title: Cloning - 1999 - Khun Copy Khun - Thai Movie
sources.description: When Dr. George brings his Human Cloning Experiment to Thailand, he is secretly funded by hospital support. He hopes that if the experiment succeeds, he will become a millionaire selling cloned organs. Niwat is a programmer and workaholic that Dr. George has abducted to take part in the experiment. Niwat is cloned, and dubbed B-7. But B-7 is mentally unbalanced, and is soon running rampant, trying to stay alive. Dr. George must head out after him, knowing that he will have to destroy his greatest creation when they finally cross paths.
